oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Crazy Water Crystals Program #12
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Crazy Water Crystals program #12, sponsored by the Crazy Water Crystal company. Hosted by Bill Karn (name unconfirmed), with the Crazy Radio Gang, the Milo Twins, the Boys In Buckskin (including Elmer and Jake), Martha Jordan (real name Dorothy Martha), Ritchie, and Doc.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Crazy Radio Gang; Martha Jordan; Milo Twins; Boys In Buckskin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Theme -- Opening statement (Bill Karn) -- Turkey In The Straw (Ritchie fiddle) -- Crazy Water Crystals commercial (Bill Karn) -- Bill Karn introduces Martha Jordan -- On A Little Bamboo Bridge (Martha Jordan) -- Crazy Water Crystals commercial (Bill Karn) -- Bill Karn introduces the Boys In Buckskin -- There's A Round-Up In The Sky (Boys In Buckskin) -- Bill Karn and Ritchie talk -- Bill Karn introduces Doc -- Nagasaki (Doc banjo) -- Crazy Water Crystals offer (Bill Karn) -- Bill Karn introduces the Milo Twins -- Corrine, Corrina (Milo Twins) -- Closing statement (Bill Karn) -- Theme
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Milo Twins; Milo, Edwin, 1916-1965; Milo, Edward, 1916-1978; Boys In Buckskin (Musical group)
